40
00:03:15,479 --> 00:03:16,240
and establish him as the heir!

41
00:03:16,320 --> 00:03:18,119
Bastards!

42
00:03:18,160 --> 00:03:20,039
This is the nation's foundation,

43
00:03:20,039 --> 00:03:22,440
Your Majesty!

44
00:03:35,479 --> 00:03:36,240
Court is adjourned!

45
00:03:37,479 --> 00:03:38,360
