95
00:07:20,000 --> 00:07:22,519
to hurry and get ready to study.

96
00:07:22,600 --> 00:07:26,000
Ming'er is not going to study?

97
00:07:26,000 --> 00:07:27,880
In the first place, she's the youngest

98
