She could not get up in the morning.

99
00:07:30,359 --> 00:07:32,040
Second…

100
00:07:32,880 --> 00:07:35,200
Second, her concubine mother just passed away.

101
00:07:35,279 --> 00:07:36,679
If she goes to the academy,

102
00:07:36,679 --> 00:07:38,880
she would just be unfocused.

103
00:07:38,920 --> 00:07:40,839
This time, even the Lordling

104
00:07:40,839 --> 00:07:41,760
from Lord Qi's House

105
00:07:41,799 --> 00:07:44,000
will come to our manor to study,

106
00:07:44,000 --> 00:07:46,320
what a heavenly honor.

107
00:07:46,399 --> 00:07:48,519
In the future, our Young Master and the Lordling

108
00:07:48,519 --> 00:07:51,559
will be classmates.

109
00:07:51,600 --> 00:07:53,359
