Changbai says Second Brother Gu will come too.

111
00:07:56,079 --> 00:07:57,279
I'm just worried about this.

112
00:07:58,200 --> 00:08:00,279
That child comes from a great house,

113
00:08:00,320 --> 00:08:01,920
but his manners are imperfect.

114
00:08:01,920 --> 00:08:02,920
I don't want him to influence

115
00:08:02,959 --> 00:08:03,839
our Changbai for the worse.

116
00:08:04,239 --> 00:08:05,519
But thankfully he's not coming anymore,

117
00:08:05,559 --> 00:08:07,959
he's going to the White Deer Academy for study.

118
00:08:08,200 --> 00:08:09,079
