121
00:08:15,119 --> 00:08:17,920
will help her sorrow fade.

122
00:08:18,000 --> 00:08:20,720
Second, she needs to understand some reasons too,

123
00:08:20,720 --> 00:08:24,000
so she can be enlightened and learned.

124
00:08:24,040 --> 00:08:25,720
Mother, you are right.

125
00:08:25,720 --> 00:08:27,239
When the scholar is here,

126
00:08:27,239 --> 00:08:29,920
we will have them go greet him.

127
00:08:29,920 --> 00:08:32,919
I've loathed the madding crowd since I was a boy

128
00:08:33,320 --> 00:08:37,799
While hills and mountains have filled me with joy.

129
00:08:37,840 --> 00:08:40,799
By mistake I sought mundane careers

130
00:08:40,799 --> 00:08:44,799
And got entrapped in them for thirty years.

131
00:08:44,799 --> 00:08:48,719
Birds in the cage would long for wooded hills;

132
00:08:48,719 --> 00:08:52,799
Fish in the pond would yearn for flowing rills.

133
00:08:52,799 --> 00:08:56,359
So I reclaim the land in southern fields

134
00:08:56,400 --> 00:09:00,760
To suit my bent for reaping farmland yields.

135
00:09:00,799 --> 00:09:04,159
My farm contains a dozen mu of ground;

136
00:09:04,200 --> 00:09:07,719
My cottage has eight or nine rooms around.

137
00:09:07,719 --> 00:09:11,080
The elm and willow cover backside eaves

138
00:09:11,200 --> 00:09:14,840
While peach and plum trees shade my yard with leaves.

139
00:09:15,799 --> 00:09:19,200
The distant village dimly looms somewhere,

140
00:09:19,200 --> 00:09:23,679
With smoke from chimneys drifting in the air.

141
00:09:23,799 --> 00:09:27,000
In silent country lanes a stray dog barks;

142
00:09:27,000 --> 00:09:31,599
Amid the mulberry trees cocks crow with larks.

143
00:09:31,640 --> 00:09:35,359
My house is free from worldly moil or gloom

144
00:09:35,400 --> 00:09:39,760
While ease and quiet permeate my private room.

145
00:09:39,760 --> 00:09:43,599
When I escape from bitter strife with men,

146
00:09:43,599 --> 00:09:47,719
I live a free and easy life again.

147
00:09:47,799 --> 00:09:48,840
Master,

148
00:09:50,799 --> 00:09:51,880
Take care.

149
00:09:52,599 --> 00:09:53,840
I've got it. Take care!

