00:27:53,719 --> 00:27:54,520
The difference

564
00:27:54,560 --> 00:27:55,599
between the two is great.

565
00:27:56,359 --> 00:27:57,800
These two older sisters of mine.

566
00:27:57,800 --> 00:27:59,160
I dare not ask them to do anything.

567
00:28:00,359 --> 00:28:01,719
Just as long as they don't harm me,

568
00:28:01,719 --> 00:28:03,280
I am satisfied.

569
00:28:03,959 --> 00:28:05,599
You're wrong though.

570
00:28:05,599 --> 00:28:07,280
Old Madam dotes on you the most.

571
00:28:07,319 --> 00:28:09,040
No one can harm you.

572
00:28:09,040 --> 00:28:11,560
Yes, Grandmother dotes on me the most.

573
00:28:11,640 --> 00:28:12,880
If she finds out

574
00:28:12,880 --> 00:28:15,640
my writing is so bad and I require someone to help me,

575
00:28:15,680 --> 00:28:17,319
she will be very upset.

576
00:28:17,319 --> 00:28:19,920
I'll accompany you when you write it then.

577
00:28:19,920 --> 00:28:20,719
Sixth Sister!

578
00:28:26,079 --> 00:28:27,959
Greetings,Young Lord.

579
00:28:30,280 --> 00:28:31,920
Your two elder sisters

580
00:28:31,920 --> 00:28:33,119
both call me “Yuanruo”.

581
00:28:33,839 --> 00:28:35,079
So why are you so formal?

582
00:28:42,359 --> 00:28:44,599
Sixth Sister, though it's cold lately,

583
00:28:45,000 --> 00:28:47,760
Madam Wu

584
00:28:47,760 --> 00:28:48,599
of Count Yongchang

585
00:28:48,920 --> 00:28:50,280
has founded a polo field

586
00:28:50,280 --> 00:28:51,800
outside Xinzheng Gate.

587
00:28:52,520 --> 00:28:55,079
There are screens on all sides and

588
00:28:55,079 --> 00:28:57,199
people can play polo in it.

589
00:28:57,199 --> 00:28:58,599
The goals are set lower by half.

590
00:28:58,599 --> 00:28:59,760
Quite fun.

591
00:28:59,760 --> 00:29:00,680
Has anyone from your manor been there before?

592
00:29:03,319 --> 00:29:04,119
We have not.

593
00:29:05,520 --> 00:29:06,439
Good then.

594
00:29:06,439 --> 00:29:07,359
Next time,

595
00:29:07,760 --> 00:29:08,800
I will ask their Sixth Brother

596
00:29:08,800 --> 00:29:09,880
to send an invitation here.

597
00:29:15,239 --> 00:29:16,719
By the way,

598
00:29:16,719 --> 00:29:19,000
Madam Wu also set up some rewards.

599
00:29:19,439 --> 00:29:22,160
They're all nice game ornaments.

600
00:29:22,280 --> 00:29:24,359
You are sure to like them, Sixth Sister.

601
00:29:26,040 --> 00:29:27,040
None of us sisters

602
00:29:27,040 --> 00:29:28,479
know how to play Polo.

603
00:29:28,520 --> 00:29:30,040
You needn't trouble yourself with it, Young Lord.

604
00:29:30,839 --> 00:29:33,040
It's no trouble. No trouble at all!

605
00:29:34,280 --> 00:29:35,560
It only takes the time

606
00:29:35,560 --> 00:29:36,680
to drink a cup of tea to reach the count manor.

607
00:29:42,880 --> 00:29:44,000
It's getting late.

608
00:29:44,000 --> 00:29:45,760
We need to return to the courtyard for the meal.

609
00:29:47,040 --> 00:29:47,920
Yes.

610
00:29:50,560 --> 00:29:52,560
Today,

611
00:29:54,719 --> 00:29:55,640
why are you dismissed so late?

612
00:29:57,040 --> 00:29:59,000
Scholar Zhuang said we did not wrote well.

613
00:29:59,000 --> 00:30:00,760
and needs to transcribe the book.

614
00:30:01,439 --> 00:30:03,199
Again?

615
00:30:05,040 --> 00:30:06,719
Then let me do half of it for you.

616
00:30:06,719 --> 00:30:08,520
I can imitate your writing.

617
00:30:08,560 --> 00:30:10,760
The Scholar punished me to transcribe

618
00:30:11,000 --> 00:30:12,839
and it's for my improvement.

619
00:30:12,880 --> 00:30:15,239
I will just do it myself.

620
00:30:16,040 --> 00:30:18,880
Xiaotao, let's not delay.

621
00:30:20,400 --> 00:30:21,959
Wait.

622
00:30:25,520 --> 00:30:26,160
These are fruits

623
00:30:26,160 --> 00:30:27,959
sent in by the Yangzhou Office.

624
00:30:27,959 --> 00:30:30,079
I hear they're only available every summer.

625
00:30:30,119 --> 00:30:31,359
This batch was frozen in the ice cave

626
00:30:31,359 --> 00:30:33,920
and when you eat them in winter, it'll still be fresh.

627
00:30:50,040 --> 00:30:52,079
Try one,

628
00:30:52,079 --> 00:30:54,000
and tell me if you like the flavor.

629
00:31:03,239 --> 00:31:04,680
Young Lord is not accustomed to it.

630
00:31:04,680 --> 00:31:06,959
That's not how you peel the water caltrop.

631
00:31:28,479 --> 00:31:29,880
Miss, look!

632
00:31:34,560 --> 00:31:37,719
Hurry to put it away!

633
00:32:01,280 --> 00:32:03,439
Such a nice brush for me to use

634
00:32:03,439 --> 00:32:04,160
is a waste.

635
00:32:05,760 --> 00:32:07,160
Why did Young Lord give you a brush?

636
00:32:07,160 --> 00:32:08,760
He should've given you more water caltrops instead.

637
00:32:08,760 --> 00:32:09,719
They're powdery and sweet.

638
00:32:11,400 --> 00:32:12,920
Water caltrops in the winter are a rare commodity.

639
00:32:12,959 --> 00:32:14,839
There couldn't be many more to be found.

640
00:32:14,880 --> 00:32:16,280
Young Lord is afraid that my brush isn't good

641
00:32:16,280 --> 00:32:18,319
so I can't write well.

642
00:32:19,040 --> 00:32:21,160
Young Lord is quite muddled.

643
00:32:21,199 --> 00:32:22,079
Your writing,

644
00:32:22,119 --> 00:32:23,719
no matter how great the brush, it's still bad.

645
00:32:23,760 --> 00:32:26,680
Nonsense. It's not that bad.

646
00:32:26,680 --> 00:32:28,199
That's not nonsense,though.

647
00:32:28,239 --> 00:32:29,439
Old Madam

648
00:32:29,439 --> 00:32:30,640
teaches you to ride the horse

649
00:32:30,680 --> 00:32:31,959
As teach you to practice writing, too.

650
00:32:31,959 --> 00:32:33,079
Whatever moon-and-stars ball skills,

651
00:32:33,079 --> 00:32:34,439
you can master them

652
00:32:34,439 --> 00:32:36,000
right away.

653
00:32:36,079 --> 00:32:37,599
It's just this calligraphy.

654
00:32:37,599 --> 00:32:38,640
You blame the brush

655
00:32:38,680 --> 00:32:40,079
and you blame the ink.

656
00:32:40,119 --> 00:32:41,520
And you even blame the paper,

657
00:32:41,520 --> 00:32:43,880
and nothing ever comes out very well.

658
00:32:44,359 --> 00:32:46,239
Some things you just can't do well.

659
00:32:46,239 --> 00:32:48,040
I was born incapable,

660
00:32:48,119 --> 00:32:50,000
so it's better not to put much hope in it.

661
00:32:50,079 --> 00:32:50,920
I don't understand.

662
00:32:50,920 --> 00:32:51,920
Do you mean the writing?

663
00:32:59,280 --> 00:33:01,319
Young Lord is like an eagle.

664
00:33:01,319 --> 00:33:03,079
The mighty eagle.

665
00:33:03,079 --> 00:33:04,160
It is meant to soar over

666
00:33:04,160 --> 00:33:05,839
the majestic mountains and high ridges.

667
00:33:06,680 --> 00:33:08,880
I am just a swift under the roof eaves.

668
00:33:08,880 --> 00:33:10,119
I can only watch from afar.

669
00:33:13,319 --> 00:33:14,680
Since we were not born into the same nest,

670
00:33:15,719 --> 00:33:17,199
I won't hope to be with him.

671
00:33:22,839 --> 00:33:24,359
Why not?

672
00:33:24,359 --> 00:33:27,119
You're the best Miss in the world!

673
00:33:30,199 --> 00:33:31,680
If I were to think it like you,

674
00:33:31,680 --> 00:33:33,160
I would be deceiving myself.

675
00:33:35,880 --> 00:33:37,199
Pear blossoms fall in the courtyard

676
00:33:37,199 --> 00:33:38,239
overflowing with moonlight.

677
00:33:38,880 --> 00:33:41,880
Willow catkins are draping the pond with a light wind.

678
00:33:43,680 --> 00:33:45,640
Yan Tongshu's poetry is so great.

679
00:33:46,640 --> 00:33:48,000
You understand Minister Yan very well.

680
00:33:48,040 --> 00:33:49,439
If he were still alive,

681
00:33:49,839 --> 00:33:51,119
he would deem you his soulmate.

682
00:33:52,239 --> 00:33:53,239
What nonsense are you spouting?

683
00:33:55,280 --> 00:33:56,760
Where are the catkins?

684
00:33:56,760 --> 00:33:58,439
Putting on a fake elegant air!

685
00:33:58,439 --> 00:33:59,760
You people from Linqige just like to

686
00:33:59,760 --> 00:34:01,359
speak words when you see human

687
00:34:01,359 --> 00:34:02,880
and bark when you see dogs.

688
00:34:04,640 --> 00:34:06,719
Fifth Sister, you only know a few words

689
00:34:06,719 --> 00:34:08,439
and you still are bold enough to tell me off?

690
00:34:09,080 --> 00:34:10,040
I wonder who the laughable one is.

691
00:34:11,959 --> 00:34:13,840
Since the old times,

692
00:34:13,879 --> 00:34:15,760
we girls who were born from the legitimate wife

693
00:34:15,760 --> 00:34:17,520
learn to manage house and be the madam of a manor.

694
00:34:17,959 --> 00:34:20,199
Not like you, born from a concubine.

695
00:34:20,280 --> 00:34:21,479
You can only rely on your coquetry

696
00:34:21,479 --> 00:34:24,000
to be singing of the wind and the moon.

697
00:34:28,679 --> 00:34:31,000
Fifth Sister, you are just envious of me,

698
00:34:31,760 --> 00:34:33,040
and hiding behind your birth as a legitimate one.

699
00:34:34,600 --> 00:34:36,959
Envious? Why should I envy you?

700
00:34:38,120 --> 00:34:39,520
You're envious that Brother Yuanruo and I

701
00:34:39,520 --> 00:34:41,560
can discuss poetry happily.

702
00:34:41,879 --> 00:34:43,080
While you,

703
00:34:43,080 --> 00:34:44,679
putting on your air of being born from the legitimate wife,

704
00:34:45,040 --> 00:34:47,360
you couldn't even talk to him.

705
00:35:05,280 --> 00:35:06,520
Fifth Miss, what are you doing?

706
00:35:06,520 --> 00:35:07,639
That belongs to my miss.

707
00:35:12,159 --> 00:35:14,000
Look at this brush.

708
00:35:14,000 --> 00:35:15,120
Does it look nice, Fourth Sister.

709
00:35:16,080 --> 00:35:17,000
Look at this.

710
00:35:17,719 --> 00:35:19,399
This brush must be

711
00:35:19,399 --> 00:35:21,320
made from the violet rabbit hair

712
00:35:21,320 --> 00:35:22,439
of the northern border.

713
00:35:23,360 --> 00:35:25,800
Shaped like a willow leaf, great for making a sharp stroke.

714
00:35:25,800 --> 00:35:26,719
And this brush pot.

715
00:35:27,159 --> 00:35:29,520
It's made of rhino's horn.

716
00:35:29,520 --> 00:35:30,239
Oh, right.

717
00:35:36,199 --> 00:35:38,120
How crisp is that sound?

718
00:35:38,120 --> 00:35:42,000
That can only be the rosewood.

719
00:35:42,040 --> 00:35:43,040
No wonder it's so crisp.

720
00:35:50,840 --> 00:35:52,479
Sixth Sister's items

721
00:35:52,479 --> 00:35:54,120
are always granted to her by Grandmother.

722
00:35:54,120 --> 00:35:55,280
What's that to you?

723
00:35:56,360 --> 00:35:58,159
Grandmother is always plain.

724
00:35:58,159 --> 00:35:59,199
Why would she have such precious items?

725
00:35:59,199 --> 00:36:00,560
They are gifted to her by Brother Yuanruo.

726
00:36:01,439 --> 00:36:02,239
You can have it.

727
00:36:02,879 --> 00:36:04,159
What?

728
00:36:04,639 --> 00:36:05,239
Young Lord

729
00:36:05,239 --> 00:36:07,280
took pity on my bad writing

730
00:36:07,280 --> 00:36:09,399
and that I was punished by the Scholar

731
00:36:09,399 --> 00:36:10,520
to transcribe “Salt- Iron Discourses”.

732
00:36:11,120 --> 00:36:12,959
Hence, he gave this brush to me.

733
00:36:12,959 --> 00:36:14,760
He said that if the brush was better so

734
00:36:14,760 --> 00:36:16,120
I could write better too.

735
00:36:17,679 --> 00:36:19,719
That bad penmanship of yours.

736
00:36:19,719 --> 00:36:20,919
Even if you're gifted with His Majesty's brushes,

737
00:36:20,959 --> 00:36:22,159
you won't do it any better.

738
00:36:22,399 --> 00:36:24,439
Don't worry about it.

739
00:36:24,439 --> 00:36:25,879
The issue is you don't have this brush!

740
00:36:26,239 --> 00:36:27,959
It sounds like you have one.

741
00:36:27,959 --> 00:36:28,879
I didn't see Brother Yuanruo

742
00:36:28,919 --> 00:36:29,760
give you two of them.

743
00:36:29,800 --> 00:36:30,879
I don't care at all.

744
00:36:31,239 --> 00:36:33,280
Frankly, Fourth Sister is right.

745
00:36:33,280 --> 00:36:35,199
If you can write the characters well,

746
00:36:35,199 --> 00:36:37,239
even if you write on sand

747
00:36:37,239 --> 00:36:38,120
with a tree branch,

748
00:36:38,120 --> 00:36:39,239
you can still write well.

749
00:36:40,080 --> 00:36:41,560
With calligraphy like mine,

750
00:36:41,560 --> 00:36:42,760
Even if it's a brush from His Majesty,

751
00:36:42,760 --> 00:36:43,560
it's still useless.

752
00:36:45,199 --> 00:36:46,520
So these two brushes you

753
00:36:46,520 --> 00:36:48,159
can have one each.

754
00:36:48,560 --> 00:36:49,479
Then it's a pair.

755
00:36:50,360 --> 00:36:51,239
That will do better justice

756
00:36:51,280 --> 00:36:52,719
to Young Lord's excellent brushes.

757
00:36:57,760 --> 00:36:58,520
Thanks.

758
00:37:03,479 --> 00:37:04,159
Let's go!

759
00:37:18,879 --> 00:37:19,639
The Young Lord

760
00:37:19,639 --> 00:37:21,399
likes that Ming'er?

761
00:37:23,479 --> 00:37:25,719
Who said he liked her?

762
00:37:25,719 --> 00:37:27,719
He's just kind at heart

763
00:37:27,719 --> 00:37:28,879
and pitied her foolishness.

764
00:37:32,159 --> 00:37:32,719
But what if

765
00:37:32,719 --> 00:37:34,719
he actually likes the foolish kind.

766
00:37:34,719 --> 00:37:37,239
Don't be too smart.

767
00:37:37,679 --> 00:37:39,080
Mother, you're…

768
00:37:41,679 --> 00:37:43,439
If he really likes her,

769
00:37:43,439 --> 00:37:44,760
how could she bear to give

770
00:37:44,760 --> 00:37:47,040
the Young Lord's gifts to us?

771
00:37:49,239 --> 00:37:50,520
That's because she can't tell the difference.

772
00:37:51,639 --> 00:37:54,159
She's just a concubine's daughter.

773
00:37:54,159 --> 00:37:57,120
How can she covet the sole heir of Qi House?

774
00:37:58,399 --> 00:37:59,919
But you are also a daughter of a concubine.

775
00:38:00,760 --> 00:38:03,080
How am I the same as her?

776
00:38:03,080 --> 00:38:04,120
I'm your daughter,

777
00:38:04,560 --> 00:38:05,879
the Fourth Miss of the Sheng family.

778
00:38:06,439 --> 00:38:08,479
I live a life more noble than the legitimate daughter

779
00:38:08,479 --> 00:38:10,600
and I placed first at the last poetry match.

780
00:38:10,600 --> 00:38:11,919
Who doesn't respect me?

781
00:38:12,760 --> 00:38:13,800
How can that Little Sixth Sheng

782
00:38:13,800 --> 00:38:15,040
bear comparison with me?

783
00:38:15,040 --> 00:38:16,439
Yes, yes,

784
00:38:16,439 --> 00:38:18,600
when my daughter marries into the Qi family,

785
00:38:19,080 --> 00:38:20,560
we'll make a rise in life.

786
00:39:02,840 --> 00:39:04,120
Second Brother Gu is here!

787
00:39:04,159 --> 00:39:04,800
Second Brother Gu.

788
00:39:04,800 --> 00:39:06,199
Changfeng, Zecheng.

789
00:39:10,560 --> 00:39:11,639
Slow down.

790
00:39:14,120 --> 00:39:15,399
Why did you only bring Shitou?

791
00:39:15,399 --> 00:39:16,239
Where is the baggage?

792
00:39:18,320 --> 00:39:19,959
You shouldn't go back empty-handed.

793
00:39:20,000 --> 00:39:21,239
Just a few boxes

794
00:39:21,239 --> 00:39:23,080
and a new family member?

795
00:39:27,360 --> 00:39:29,520
What do you mean by a family member?

796
00:39:31,679 --> 00:39:34,600
I met her in Bianjing

797
00:39:34,600 --> 00:39:35,800
and I found her pitiful so

798
00:39:36,320 --> 00:39:37,919
I gave her some silver to dismiss her.

799
00:39:39,040 --> 00:39:41,000
Then his sinister older brother

800
00:39:41,040 --> 00:39:42,320
tricked away everything from her.

801
00:39:43,159 --> 00:39:44,199
And she ran to White Deer Cave Academy

802
00:39:44,199 --> 00:39:45,000
to seek me.

803
00:39:45,800 --> 00:39:46,840
Her older brother

804
00:39:46,840 --> 00:39:48,040
spent all the money

805
00:39:48,479 --> 00:39:49,360
and jumped down from the cliff and died.

806
00:39:49,959 --> 00:39:51,000
I saw how pitiful she was

807
00:39:51,000 --> 00:39:52,639
with nowhere to go, so

808
00:39:54,959 --> 00:39:56,000
I took her in.

809
00:40:03,320 --> 00:40:05,120
She didn't come with me.

810
00:40:05,120 --> 00:40:07,600
I settled her and some chests

811
00:40:07,600 --> 00:40:08,879
in another place.

812
00:40:09,800 --> 00:40:11,479
These are of no importance!

813
00:40:11,879 --> 00:40:13,679
Scholar Zhuang opens the academy

814
00:40:13,679 --> 00:40:14,520
at 6'clock and he is strict

815
00:40:14,520 --> 00:40:16,199
so we can't be late.

816
00:40:16,520 --> 00:40:17,120
Han Niu.

817
00:40:17,679 --> 00:40:19,080
Shitou,

818
00:40:19,080 --> 00:40:19,959
there's nothing here.

819
00:40:20,560 --> 00:40:22,120
Go with them

820
00:40:22,120 --> 00:40:22,959
and help tidy up.

821
00:40:23,000 --> 00:40:24,000
Don't let them laze.

822
00:40:24,040 --> 00:40:24,879
Okay, Master.

823
00:40:25,520 --> 00:40:27,280
Brother Gu, where did this handkerchief come from?

824
00:40:27,919 --> 00:40:29,040
What great embroidery work!

825
00:40:29,760 --> 00:40:31,280
Can't be that top prostitute Wei embroidered it personally?

826
00:40:31,840 --> 00:40:32,560
I haven no use for it.

827
00:40:32,560 --> 00:40:34,320
If you like it, take it then.

828
00:40:35,840 --> 00:40:36,679
Hurry up now.

829
00:40:36,719 --> 00:40:37,600
It's time.

830
00:40:38,600 --> 00:40:40,600
Miss, don't sleep anymore.

831
00:40:41,840 --> 00:40:42,840
Why do you sleep so much?

832
00:40:42,959 --> 00:40:44,040
Fourth and Fifth Misses

833
00:40:44,040 --> 00:40:45,120
never sleep much as you do.

834
00:41:08,600 --> 00:41:10,439
Stop fanning.

835
00:41:12,879 --> 00:41:14,639
Stop fanning.

836
00:41:19,320 --> 00:41:20,560
Yuanruo!

837
00:41:21,959 --> 00:41:23,040
What are you doing here?

838
00:41:23,879 --> 00:41:24,959
Second Uncle?

839
00:41:25,040 --> 00:41:26,840
It's what I should ask you about.

840
00:41:27,520 --> 00:41:28,239
Come here.

841
00:41:31,399 --> 00:41:32,280
Second Uncle,

842
00:41:32,280 --> 00:41:34,399
I'm studying here.

843
00:41:34,399 --> 00:41:35,399
Hey, Young Lord,

844
00:41:35,399 --> 00:41:36,800
why did you call him Second Uncle here?

845
00:41:37,719 --> 00:41:39,239
We are relatives back up the generations.

846
00:41:39,239 --> 00:41:40,000
And at our generation,

847
00:41:40,000 --> 00:41:41,080
I'm his nephew.

848
00:41:43,520 --> 00:41:45,280
Second Uncle,

849
00:41:45,280 --> 00:41:46,919
this is the Sixth Daughter of the Sheng family.

850
00:41:47,360 --> 00:41:48,520
Sixth Miss.

851
00:41:48,520 --> 00:41:49,360
Hello, Second Uncle.

852
00:41:53,120 --> 00:41:54,760
We can't delay it.

853
00:41:54,760 --> 00:41:56,320
Scholar Shuang will punish us

854
00:41:56,399 --> 00:41:57,600
if we're late.

855
00:41:58,959 --> 00:42:00,959
But he won't be early today.

856
00:42:00,959 --> 00:42:02,000
Since you're sleepy,

857
00:42:02,000 --> 00:42:03,719
go nap a bit more.

858
00:42:03,719 --> 00:42:04,600
Then you can come back.

859
00:42:05,360 --> 00:42:06,520
Xiaotao.

860
00:42:07,040 --> 00:42:08,280
Take care of your Sixth Miss.

861
00:42:08,280 --> 00:42:09,080
Yes.

862
00:42:10,639 --> 00:42:11,399
Sixth Sister,

863
00:42:11,399 --> 00:42:12,239
we are taking our leave.

864
00:42:13,080 --> 00:42:13,719
Let's go!

865
00:42:15,840 --> 00:42:16,479
Let's go.

866
00:42:20,520 --> 00:42:21,600
Alright, Miss,

867
00:42:21,719 --> 00:42:23,439
you got the Second Brother's permission,

868
00:42:23,439 --> 00:42:25,159
so lean on me to nap more.

869
00:42:26,439 --> 00:42:28,159
You really thought it was about nap?

870
00:42:29,840 --> 00:42:31,000
Second Brother was…

871
00:42:31,000 --> 00:42:31,679
was trying to

872
00:42:33,159 --> 00:42:34,520
help me avoid suspicion,

873
00:42:34,560 --> 00:42:35,600
in case others that see me

874
00:42:35,600 --> 00:42:38,800
with the Young Lord together and gossip.

875
00:42:39,520 --> 00:42:40,879
When Young Lord was here,

876
00:42:40,879 --> 00:42:42,159
why didn't you tell me?

877
00:42:43,159 --> 00:42:44,560
If this happens again,

878
00:42:44,560 --> 00:42:46,120
I'm going to kick you out.

879
00:42:46,919 --> 00:42:48,439
Fourth Miss and Fifth Miss

880
00:42:48,520 --> 00:42:50,320
often laugh and talk with the Young Lord.

881
00:42:50,679 --> 00:42:52,239
Last year's Lantern Festival,

882
00:42:52,719 --> 00:42:54,239
we ran into the Young Lord while strolling

883
00:42:54,239 --> 00:42:55,600
and both the Master and Madam saw.

884
00:42:56,000 --> 00:42:57,439
Fourth and Fifth Misses

885
00:42:57,439 --> 00:42:59,360
even pestered the Young Lord to buy some lanterns.

886
00:43:00,120 --> 00:43:01,879
You were the only one who didn't want to accept it.

887
00:43:02,800 --> 00:43:03,919
We're different.

888
00:43:04,919 --> 00:43:06,000
The two of them,

889
00:43:06,360 --> 00:43:07,560
one has dignity

890
00:43:07,560 --> 00:43:08,479
while the other has the status.

891
00:43:09,040 --> 00:43:10,679
They have parents to take care of them.

892
00:43:11,280 --> 00:43:12,879
I only have Grandmother,

893
00:43:12,879 --> 00:43:14,919
and I can't cause trouble for her, right?

894
00:43:16,520 --> 00:43:17,120
Yes.

895
00:43:22,959 --> 00:43:23,919
Young Master Gu is already back

896
00:43:23,919 --> 00:43:24,800
after finishing his studies.

897
00:43:27,879 --> 00:43:30,159
My mother has been deceased for so long now.
